{"tid":2395350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"此「武」非彼武？加拿大駐中使館訂作「Wuhan蝙蝠」T恤引爆外交爭端　北京怒嗆給交代","createTime":"2021-02-05T00:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T01:40:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0c99a6b72e6fbec5b95731632988c0cf9c07ec5a","tid":2395350,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:09:53.000Z","msg":"此「武」非彼武？加拿大駐中使館訂作「Wuhan蝙蝠」T恤引爆外交爭端　北京怒嗆給交代<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/3453711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F3453711&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=b91ac22b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/3453711</a><br />\n<br />\n近日有成衣廠商在網路上檢舉稱，加拿大駐中使館去年訂製的一款上衣，以蝙蝠圖案搭配武漢字樣，事涉新冠病毒起源的敏感議題，在WHO專家團赴武漢調查之際，旋即在中國掀起輿論風波，更驚動中方嚴正提出交涉，要求加拿大徹查此事並「給個明確交代」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">加拿大外交部雖連忙做出澄清，解釋所謂的「蝙蝠」圖樣，其實是向美國嘻哈團體「武當幫」（Wu-Tang Clan）的代表Logo致敬</span></span></strong>，願對由此產生的任何誤會致歉，但中國外交部發言人汪文斌3日在例行記者會上直言，難以相信使館人員身為派駐多年的高級外交官，「會如此無意識地犯這樣的低級錯誤！」顯然對加拿大的說法並不買帳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">武當與武漢</span></strong><br />\n肆虐全球的新冠疫情雖從中國武漢爆發，但北京當局迄今不肯鬆口，更屢屢試圖將「病毒起源地」之名「甩鍋」給歐、美國家。中國網友批評，加拿大使館人員訂製這款T恤，目的是暗指武漢疫情爆發與動物有所關聯，更再次建立中國人喜食野味的刻板印象。<br />\n<br />\n汪文斌強調，加拿大外交部的「誤解說」並不令人信服，「有關人員的錯誤行徑已造成惡劣影響，引發廣大中國人民的強烈反感和不滿」，要求加方嚴肅認真對待此事。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">武當幫於90年代初期在紐約發跡，被譽為有史以來最偉大的嘻哈團體之一；其Logo圖案雖與蝙蝠相似，實際上則是英文字母「Ｗ」的變體。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n巧合的是，團體以「武當」命名的靈感，來自1980年上映的香港電影《少林與武當》，樂團在首張專輯中更分為少林、武當兩派，而武當山與武漢同樣位於湖北省境內。"},{"pid":"1fe6db9b44c684d534187c0faf1a4f530cf28aec","tid":2395350,"uid":33869,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:14:52.000Z","msg":"加拿大咁識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c3ba522b8dc475a59e1d907857f346fe432757","tid":2395350,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:15:38.000Z","msg":"支那又柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b696dd23ce3380513ecb1114a39eda0482bf47d","tid":2395350,"uid":53970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"72c3ba522b8dc475a59e1d907857f346fe432757","tid":2395350,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:15:38.000Z","msg":"支那又柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:23:06.000Z","msg":"有邊次支那柒左會認錯道歉<br />\n點撚樣都屈鳩你錯先架啦"},{"pid":"17cf213d95e0b4a86a6f9d0ca880178436ecd466","tid":2395350,"uid":54975,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:26:21.000Z","msg":"撚狗<br />\n就算係武漢蝙蝠又點？ 冇貶意㗎喎，支那個名本身先係貶意啦，如果唔係啲支那狗唔使去到其他地方就話自己係香港人啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80bf9c341e8bbf0bcd4c9c683a2d96ddc2cc896","tid":2395350,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:31:06.000Z","msg":"有頭有翼就係蝙蝠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7565634c8e7e0c9c32c7d198775c05b9d39904c8","tid":2395350,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:33:54.000Z","msg":"以後無得睇batman"},{"pid":"96148d717f05c453dbd8783ac208882fce2fa178","tid":2395350,"uid":310446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:36:32.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好移民同住喺加拿大囉<br />\n夠薑取消埋加拿大籍吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823aa09026aa2992388aae09c099a2d6100e89d0","tid":2395350,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:43:57.000Z","msg":"大陸 官方都叫「新冠」肺炎<br />\n<br />\n加拿大 點知咩 武漢 同 蝙蝠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc9b9015c5d0488c98eec1e2c353637b9060289","tid":2395350,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:52:15.000Z","msg":"唔滿意咪撤僑囉"},{"pid":"524d1afacaabec47216325de9f965032e579f648","tid":2395350,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:54:01.000Z","msg":"講中左嬲嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2818d95c28a42500fcb7541d77537475e22971","tid":2395350,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:54:06.000Z","msg":"玻璃心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49830ac501cbd990cfe8341d26416237865c223a","tid":2395350,"uid":113250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:56:11.000Z","msg":"明明蝙蝠係中國自古以來不可分割的一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BWCxvz1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBWCxvz1.jpg&h=55318f6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6033896e1673d1cf89e5a3e1882a5ece9d532103","tid":2395350,"uid":183090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yc62SOm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyc62SOm.jpg&h=314a6b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2769dbd4ebcb9b337cc963c562dd860f9b4bd778","tid":2395350,"uid":263409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T00:58:22.000Z","msg":"咁都踩到你條尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ac43faae8f5851370e43aec5a1224e48729cf2","tid":2395350,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T01:04:28.000Z","msg":"乜野人咪睇到乜野野囉"},{"pid":"6cbb975d725fbc8754efd5f8b1d93ff9fd4477a7","tid":2395350,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T01:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets